This is a fantastic app! It is absolutely loaded with information on calling & hunting elk. This app really helps users learn to "speak" the elk language. The app does this by explaining the meaning behind the sounds and what each sound is trying to communicate to other elk. Once you understand this, then you know what the elk are saying and what you as the caller should say in response. Not only that, but this app is great for helping you learn how to do the calling with an elk reed. There are excellent videos that talk about tongue placement, pressure, and sounds to make with your own voice while trying to make the elk sounds with the reeds. The app also has LOTS of tactics and tips on hunting elk. It is very informative. Paul Medel is wonderful at educating elk hunters and sharing his knowledge. This app is great for any elk hunter. It is a steal at the price.has
